                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340904-226-off1268 t18340904-226-cd1269"></join>, 1 sovereign, and 1 half-sovereign, the monies of 
                     <persName id="t18340904-226-victim1343" type="victimName">
                        Thomas 
